Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be performed after SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average cycle time of SW-EIC Reject across all variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-EIC Reject and the end of the case

Name: Time elapsed from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-EIC Reject in variants ending with SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and activity SW-EIC Reject for cases where activity SW-EIC Reject occurs

Name: Average time for SW-EIC Reject when preceded by SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation versus when preceded directly by SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-EIC Reject in cases where the variant includes at least one Reviewer Invitation Reminder
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-EIC Reject' and the end of case where activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1 occurs

Name: Minimum time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-EIC Reject in rejected submissions
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-EIC Reject after the completion of SW-Checklist Completed in rejection paths
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-EIC Reject in variants that include multiple reviewer declines before SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-EIC Reject compared to the total time between SW-Reviewer Declined and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Cycle time of SW-EIC Reject in variants that involve Assign a Different Editor versus those that do not
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-EIC Reject' and the end of case where activity 'Assign a Different Editor occurs

Name: Average time it takes SW-EIC Reject to occur after the last occurrence of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time elapsed from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-EIC Reject in the shortest and longest rejection variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'
